Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A racing second hand,\Na shooting comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan's logic works fast on\Nhearts tired by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's case is an impossible crime!\NMoney comes and goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single\Ntruth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.71,0:00:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid but\Nhas the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:57.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Finance Company President Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Finance Company President Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:59.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I lose the {\i1}ryan-pin{\i0}?\N({\i1}ryan-pin {\i0}= two)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A {\i1}sha-bo {\i0}would make the wait pointless...\N({\i1}sha-bo {\i0}= double-pair)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! Are you messing\Nwith my pieces again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. You're doing\Nwell tonight. Consider it a handicap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ron{\i0}! (winning move)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Menchin{\i0}, {\i1}ipeiko{\i0}, {\i1}dora{\i0}, {\i1}dora{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a {\i1}baiman{\i0}! ({\i1}baiman {\i0}= double)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving, Okano?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I have no luck tonight.\NI'll be off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we need another player...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask Hida-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hida-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He runs that finance company.\NHe loves Mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:46.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,President's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:53.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hida Mitsuhiro (53)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 million. I'm all smiles tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Hida Financial.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Hida-{\i1}san{\i0}! You're still there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Hasegawa-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need another player,\Nso I thought I'd ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there once\NI'm done counting this money!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there in half an hour!\NPlay without me until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Says it'll be thirty minutes\Nand to keep playing until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, then I'll play until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, you won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering where you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought him here,\Ndidn't you, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, would you wanna play\Nfor half an hour or so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that stupid,\Ngloomy grownup game!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ron{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A {\i1}dai-san-gen{\i0}, {\i1}su-an-ko{\i0},\Nand {\i1}tsui-i-so{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A triple {\i1}yakuman{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A triple {\i1}yakuman{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Hida-{\i1}san{\i0}, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give him a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird, he's not answering.\NBut his lights are still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, yeah, he was strangely\Nflustered when I called him earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he was robbed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hida-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in there, Hida-{\i1}san{\i0}? Hida-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:37.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Minamisawa Hisayoshi (34)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your boss never showed up,\Nso we came to get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left my cell phone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where's your boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His office, I'd assume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a master key?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd never make a master key;\Nthe vault's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll just have to bust it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good. He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deceased is\NHida Mitsuhiro-{\i1}san{\i0}, 53.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cause was potassium\Ncyanide-induced suffocation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died some time\Nbetween 7:00 and 7:30 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Takagi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key on the desk opens this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the fact that the windows\Nwere locked from the inside
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,means this was an impossible\Ncrime and a locked-room murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The security tape has\Nyou leaving at 7:04 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he locks the door and returns\Nto his office to balance accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two hours later...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you folks show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who were the two people\Nwith you when you left?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you page me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:34.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujii Takako (29)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was having fun\Ndoing karaoke with friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:39.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Iino Hiroshi (31)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone murdered your boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. So the cretin finally\Ngot what he deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure is a lot\Nof money strewn about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's biting his nails.\NIs it a habit of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Habit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, did your boss have any habits?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Habits?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like when he counts\Nmoney or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,\Nhe always spread the bills like a fan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then licked\Nhis right thumb like so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave these bills to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer was you, lino-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You laced the bills with poison in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Detective Mori said, poison was\Nfound on the victim's right thumb
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and several of the bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd I tell ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the poison on the\Nbills was shaped like his thumbprint,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it was likely his\Nthumb that put it there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the coffee I gave him\Njust before I left for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then {\i1}you're {\i0}the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably smeared poison\Nall over the cup handle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no poison was found\Non the cup or in the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only found poison on the\Nvictim's thumb, several bills,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and two other places--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the inside door knob\Nand the lock above it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just like on the bills, the poison\Nwas in the shape of his thumbprint,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it seems he touched them\Nwith the poison on his thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, he said the\Nvictim was flustered on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if he left the room halfway\Nthrough counting the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,touched something with poison on it,\Nreturned to this room,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and locked the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how'd they get him\Nto touch whatever it was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:09:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you haven't touched\Nanything since you arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I've touched\Nwas this cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I hold on to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious? I'm making tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Don't touch {\i1}anything{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't touched\Nanything else, have you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used the restroom\Nwhen I got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I used it after her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used the computer\Na little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! No dropping ashes here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy now, Mr. Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all suspects! No wandering around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all suspects! No wandering around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, I turned it on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think it's OK to shut it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shut it off!\NJust don't touch anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, one wrong key press\Nand they'll find your data...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The records of you\Nembezzling company money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embezzling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I haven't done anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you killed him\Nbecause he found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You {\i0}wanted to kill him too,\NMinamisawa-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:11:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in tears\Nwhen he blamed you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for a client defaulting on a big loan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You {\i0}were always wishing\Nhow he'd die already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if a borrower isn't gonna repay,\Nhe shouldn't borrow at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found no poison\Nanywhere in the office?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even the restroom or break room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was potassium cyanide\Nthe victim touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be wiped cleanly away\Non such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means it's\Non one of you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to ask each of you\Nto empty your pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You first, Minamisawa-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wallet, watch, house key, notebook,\Ntrain pass, and handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The handkerchief is a little damp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I just used the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Fujii-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Your handkerchief is damp, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously. I also used the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're next, lino-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And another damp handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but yours is sopping wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tend to sweat a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of their things came out positive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of their things came out positive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Absolutely no poison was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be taking my things back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I still--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Say, that person's been\Nlike that this whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mister Examiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you checked everything\Nthe victim might've touched, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you check for fingerprints, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, what if--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I thought it\Nwas strange, myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna get mad\Nif you poke around there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it! Bleach!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spill-off is fresh!\NThe killer used this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person's actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the unnatural fingerprints,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the time they\Nentered the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They manipulated and poisoned\Nthe victim in this otherwise empty office!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if by magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sneaking around again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Take him home already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, Mori-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The killer's aim\Nwas a locked-room murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran. Return to my office and\Nget the iodine from the first-aid kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer's identity will\Nemerge once we have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer got the victim to leave\Nthe room halfway through his counting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and got him to touch\Nsomething with poison on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was after he returned and locked\Nthe door that he was poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer used the victim's\Nhabit of licking his right thumb
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before counting money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, the killer was\None of you three employees
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who knew of his habit\Nand what he was doing tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! No poison was\Nfound outside this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, how did the killer\Nget him to touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:15:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain something would make\N10 out of 10 people do the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! The phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone would pick up\Na ringing phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minamisawa-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you called from outside so he'd\Npick up your poison-covered phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minamisawa-{\i1}san{\i0} bites his nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, when he came to get his phone,\Nhe picked it up with his bare hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had there been poison, he'd have\Nbeen too afraid to do such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because there'd be no telling\Nwhere it had been touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The computer, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iino-{\i1}san{\i0}! You had him turn it on\Nto check some data, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'd be no guarantee\Nhe'd turn it on with his thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what was the poison on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:16:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a way to make him\Ntouch something with his right thumb
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether he wanted to or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The demonic call the killer\Nused to lead him to his death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the teapot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teapot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer put poison\Non the knob here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right, Mori-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gas stoves on the market are\Nusually for right-handers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poison left on the left side of the\Nknob would be touched by a thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof, only this door's\Ninside knob had poison on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:17:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means he rushed out\Nwithout closing the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,touched the poison\Nin his flustered state,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then closed it when he returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So who used that trick\Nto poison the president?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who got\Nnear the stove afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you, Fujii Takako-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Just before you left,\Nyou put the teapot on the stove
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the whistle would sound\Nwhile he was counting the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You planned to wipe\Nthe poison away tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but his body was found earlier\Nthan expected and the police showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afraid the poison on the\Nstove knob would be discovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you entered the break room and\Nwiped it off with your handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that? You said yourself it\Ncouldn't be wiped away so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it {\i1}is {\i0}impossible. Assuming\Nit was an ordinary handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought the iodine, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iodine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, Inspector. Please put\Nsome iodine on her damp handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A single drop will shed\Nlight on everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just going to\Nmake a brown stain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The color disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Soaked into her handkerchief\Nis neither water nor sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sodium thiosulfate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodium thiosulfate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bleach used to remove color\Nfrom disinfectants like iodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also an antidote that neutralizes\Nthe effects of potassium chloride!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still some\Nin the restroom cabinet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:19:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bleach with a special chemical\Nthat reacts at room temperature, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the police found out,\NFujii-{\i1}san {\i0}likely went straight to the restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and soaked her\Nhandkerchief in the bleach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I was\Nfound out so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujii-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I killed\Nthat devious money-fiend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy. My man borrowed money from him
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then hung himself\Nwhen he couldn't pay it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were always saying\Nhow borrowing money is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I wouldn't have\Nbothered with revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had he borrowed money for a car,\Na house, or gambling,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:20:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was for my sake,\Nso I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always had a weak heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was in the hospital between my\Ncollege graduation and three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents died early on and I had\Nno friends because of my attitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so only he ever visited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd pay the\Nhospital bills somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I finally got better\Nand went to his apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found him dead with a\NHida Financial loan form at his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you joined the\Ncompany to get revenge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. I waited for my\Nchance this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Detective.\NHow did you know I did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be because of the left hand\Nyou kept in your coat the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always used your right hand\Nto take out cigarettes or use a lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used your left hand\Nonly once to turn the stove knob.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a heavy smoker.\NYou touch your lips when you smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afraid of that, you purposely\Nturned the knob with your left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, you kept your\Nleft hand in your pocket
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you wouldn't accidentally\Nsmear the poison on anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to think my man\Ngot me to stop smoking...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be laughing\Nin the next world...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.93,0:22:53.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Arcade
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kogoro-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see you here too often!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:22:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.85,0:23:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody'll play with me 'cuz it\Nreminds them of what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you bring a kid with you\Nto play Strip Mahjong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! Now {\i1}chi-so-ki {\i0}for a {\i1}dama-ten{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron! Go for the {\i1}sha-ki{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well, you see--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to lose the {\i1}pa-so {\i0}and use\Nthe {\i1}dora-so-machi {\i0}to get a {\i1}soku-ri{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Riichi{\i0}! (one tile to win)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.55,0:23:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right. You got an {\i1}an-ko{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right. You got an {\i1}an-ko{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tsumo{\i0}! (wild tile)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A {\i1}riichi{\i0}, {\i1}ippatsu tsumo{\i0},\N{\i1}hon-itsu{\i0}, and four {\i1}doras{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even an {\i1}ura-dora{\i0}!\NHurray! A {\i1}sanbaiman{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! Last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world\Ntaught you Mahjong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:23:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:23:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:25.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.55,0:24:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaitou #1412, who toys with\Npolice the country over...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.14,0:24:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AKA "Kaitou Kid"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is insane! No one can\Njust disappear like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.44,0:24:31.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan vs. Kaitou Kid
